OL,4,C Following the success of the SABRE-   
OL,5,C Orakle integration, The Ministry of   
OL,6,C Harmony confirms that physical        
OL,7,C banknotes are now redundant. All      
OL,8,C transactions in Xenograd are now     C
OL,9,C strictly PAY-BY-PALM.                 
OL,11,  REACTION:FSome citizens have expressed
OL,12,F "emotional distress" that images of   
OL,13,F our Great Hero, GOUJON JOHN will no   
OL,14,F longer reside in our pockets.         
OL,16,  SOLUTION:FFor those with sufficient   
OL,17,F Loyalty Ratings, DETAILING STATIONS   
OL,18,F are now open at Prodmash No.12. High- 
OL,19,F speed lasers can now engrave the      
OL,20,F Leader's likeness directly onto your  
OL,21,F payment palm.                         
OL,22,  "Now He is not just in my pocket,     
OL,23,   He is part of my hand"               
